				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
									<h2><strong>Beyond the Board </strong></h2><h3><strong>Cheese Foundations</strong></h3><ul><li>How to make cream cheese from scratch</li><li>Understanding different types of cheeses (soft, hard, spreads)</li><li>How to flavour and customise cheeses</li></ul><h3><strong>Flavour Pairing &amp; Composition</strong></h3><ul><li>How to balance flavours: creamy, salty, sweet, tangy, crunchy</li><li>Pairing cheeses with accompaniments for a complete board</li><li>Building cohesive boards instead of random combinations</li></ul><h3><strong>Board Styling &amp; Presentation</strong></h3><ul><li>Elements of a perfect grazing board</li><li>Selecting the right sized serving boards/platters</li><li>Selecting breads, crackers, fruits, nuts &amp; spreads</li><li>Quick garnishing techniques for a polished finish</li><li>How to create height, flow, and visual balance</li><li>Portioning for small vs large gatherings</li></ul>								</div>
